# ShellCheck configuration for the DSO plugin
#
# Disabled checks:
# SC1090 - Can't follow non-constant source (dynamic source paths are intentional)
# SC1091 - Not following: file not found (sourced files resolved at runtime via CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT)
